reviews.review_text: Lost Gem This chould be one of the top 5 best shows ever from the Dead! I first heard this show on the radio than found it hear. Bones disk on New Road Trips but not the first half of the show. Awsome Railroads, Bobby. Enjoy this one!
- Certainly a great performance, but it's hard for me to find shows from this era I really like.
